### 10. No Login Validation Schema — Missing Server-Side Zod Validation
**File:** [auth.ts](file:///c:/Users/DELL%20LATITUDE/Desktop/SecureGate/src/lib/auth.ts#L25-L28)

The login `authorize` function checks `!credentials?.email || !credentials?.password` but doesn't use Zod for validation. Every other endpoint uses Zod. The AGENTS.md says: *"Use Zod for server-side validation"* and *"Always validate request body"*.

**Fix:** Create a `loginSchema` in `validation.ts` and use it in `authorize`.

