### 13. Forgot Password Rate Limit Inconsistent with Spec
**File:** [forgot-password/route.ts](file:///c:/Users/DELL%20LATITUDE/Desktop/SecureGate/src/app/api/auth/forgot-password/route.ts#L24-L27)

```typescript
const { allowed } = await rateLimit(`forgot-password:${ip}`, {
  limit: 3,      // ← Spec says 5 attempts
  window: 3600,  // ← Spec says 10 minutes (600s), this is 1 hour
